@atlas C|AIRGENOME_GENOME_LAYOUT_V1_4|@C AIRGENOME_GENOME_LAYOUT_V1_4 = canonical: 15 pairs × 4 bytes = 60 B (each pair = f32 little-endian IEEE-754). Hex encoding = 120 hex chars. Pair ordering = lex on (Axis,Axis). Source: archive/v1/docs/gates.hexa §\\"GENOME SERIALIZATION\\" + spec §\\"GateGenome 60-byte struct\\". :: omega_cycle_airgenome [10*]\\n  => fully-specified canonical layout (FROZEN in v1)\\n  \|> airgenome/archive/v1/docs/gates.hexa lines 1138-1146|atlas.append.airgenome-2026-04-27.n6|65|-1|false|false
